    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 requirements for Class II devices at MRL 2. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. Relative hemolysis index predictions within 15% acceptance band across all validation operating points. Model accepted for regulatory submission supporting 510(k) predicate comparison.",
